  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/f0060658aa75a66bad1b4b85665bbbc5.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/f0060658aa75a66bad1b4b85665bbbc5.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/f0060658aa75a66bad1b4b85665bbbc5.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build and manage your growing town in this relaxing village construction and management simulator with focus on production chains and villager desires.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/1d4e7084c6114eeb13aceabe40f4fd54.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/1d4e7084c6114eeb13aceabe40f4fd54.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/1d4e7084c6114eeb13aceabe40f4fd54.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Start with nothing and grow into a bustling town. Gather and process resources and maintain your villager needs<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/d5b11de61110ea28fe2a76b5ebec5cdd.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/d5b11de61110ea28fe2a76b5ebec5cdd.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/d5b11de61110ea28fe2a76b5ebec5cdd.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect and record knowledge, research and advance through technologies, and unlock new materials and professions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/b6bfee2fdfffe0e0ea5cbd31f39b59f4.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/b6bfee2fdfffe0e0ea5cbd31f39b59f4.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/b6bfee2fdfffe0e0ea5cbd31f39b59f4.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Establish many production chains with unique processing buildings and outputs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/de882e4b99e7dfa5817ef48a71299016.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/de882e4b99e7dfa5817ef48a71299016.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/de882e4b99e7dfa5817ef48a71299016.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Everything from mining ores and crafting tools to growing crops and brewing beer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/eae89f9b02abd0a9a2e8b27c3e41c294.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=400 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/eae89f9b02abd0a9a2e8b27c3e41c294.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/eae89f9b02abd0a9a2e8b27c3e41c294.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mr. Piggles agrees.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/f31cffc166b011544e4c49ee8dd2edaa.poster.avif?t=1747052509\" width=326 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/f31cffc166b011544e4c49ee8dd2edaa.webm?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/931270/extras/f31cffc166b011544e4c49ee8dd2edaa.mp4?t=1747052509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
